  "remarks": "JSC Russian Machines (a.k.a. JSC Nizhegorodskie Avtomobili) is an industrial conglomerate owned by Oleg Deripaska. It includes Military Industrial Company and Arzamas Machine-Building Plant, which manufactures the BTR-80 amphibious armoured personnel carriers that were used by Russia during the unprovoked military aggression against Ukraine in 2022.",
